三、教學目標 Objectives


民以食為天，環境惡化、生態失衡、環境的變遷造成現今資源流失，癌症等疾病開始纏身，各種病菌叢生危害人類的生存。故本課程以環境與人類生存保健為主軸；以往環境保護只註意污染防治的工作，現在則註重避免污染的發生。更重視全球自然資源的保護及生態平衡等威脅人類生存的全球性環境問題。在生活中，建造無毒的生活空間，隨時隨地降低自己的欲求並用寬廣平等的心，維持世間萬物的永續共榮，追求不一樣的環保實踐。 


Food, environmental degradation, ecological imbalance, changes in the environment caused by the current resource loss, cancer and other diseases start-ridden, a variety of bacteria clusters endanger the survival of humanity. Therefore, this course is the environment and human health as the main survival; in the past only pay attention to environmental protection, pollution prevention and control work, now taken to avoid contamination. Pay more attention to the protection of global natural resources and ecological balance threaten the survival of mankind global environmental problems. In life, the construction of non-toxic living space, reduce their desire equal anywhere and with a broad mind, to maintain things in the world of sustainable prosperity, pursue different environmental practices. 


四、課程內容 Course Description


●整體敘述 Overall Description本課程涵蓋下列內容：1.全球環境保護    2.捍衛水資源              3.氣候變化及能源危機      4 核災、輻射防護的基本認知 5.基因改造食品    6. 食的安全--塑化劑       7.管好荷爾蒙不生病        8. 荷爾蒙是一生美麗的關鍵  9. 癌症相關報導   10.污染防治—無毒生活進度: 每一∼二週探討一主題

